column16: After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War
column17: the universe is in ruins. With the help of remaining allies
column18: the Avengers assemble once more in order to reverse Thanos' actions and restore balance to the universe.

column16: As the Avengers and their allies have continued to protect the world from threats too large for any one hero to handle
column17: a new danger has emerged from the cosmic shadows: Thanos.
